---
name: Text to Image Builder
description: Compose a text-to-image prompt from a diagram type, user subject, and style
tags: [builder, text-to-image]
inputs:
  diagram_type_prompt:
    type: string
    default: "Create a clean, polished tech diagram."
  user_prompt:
    type: string
    default: ""
  style_prompt:
    type: string
    default: ""
---
{{diagram_type_prompt}}

{{user_prompt}}

Visual style: {{style_prompt}}
